Spotify Artwork

Get album artwork for a vector of given Spotify album IDs

  1. Configure your application. Help on authorisation.

  2. Create a list of Spotify album IDs in a column called album_id, save as .tsv in the data folder.

  3. Run the scripts from the project file.

Many thanks to Charlie86 ‘s excellent ’spotifyr’ web api client for making this process much less painful.

Also thomasp85‘s excellent ’patchwork’ package for wrapping the artwork together very easily.

Last but not least, ropensci‘s ’magick’ package for simple image manipulation.
